About Us
PixelWorks Inc. is a professional design, development, and training firm. Our focus is on employing top-notch creative thinking, design approach, and functional application in every project we take on. We are also an Adobe Authorized Training Center providing instructor led software training, training support, and e-learning content development.Our company is a certified participant in the U.S. Small Business Administration's SBA 8(a) program, and is a proud Service Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Business (SDVOSB).














What We Do






Front-End Development

                            Our development team is experienced with using standards-based web technologies (HTML, CSS, DOM, and JavaScript) to create immersive front-end applications and connected visual UIs.
                          





Software Training

                            We have been training clients on Adobe software tools for more than 15 years. As an Adobe Authorized Training Provider (AATP), trust us to help you master these industry-standard tools.
                          





E-Learning Development

                            As software trainers, e-learning is in our DNA. In fact, we have been involved with building e-learning content since 2004. Contact us to discuss a custom e-learning solution for your organization.
                          






SharePoint Branding & App Dev

                           Our developers can build custom integrated styling into Master Pages & Page Layouts. We can also build immersive apps that leverage site list data with jQuery, JavaScript, CSOM, JSOM, & REST.
                          





Web & Mobile Apps

                            We build responsive web experiences that readily adapt to different devices. We also develop cross-platform mobile apps for iOS, Android, & others, using the PhoneGap Build framework.
                          





Graphic Design & Marketing

                            PixelWorks has a talented team of "creatives" that are very adept visual thinkers capable of creating award-winning designs custom suited for any visually intensive project.
                          















